# Learning loop (brain-lite)

See `harness/LEARNING_LOOP.md` for full map.

## After significant tasks (layer 1 — always)

1. Update `log.md`, `hot.md`; milestone → `.agent/MEMORY.md`
2. For reusable insight: emit LEARNING_BLOCK per `knowledge/learnings/LEARNING_BLOCK_TEMPLATE.md`
3. Ingest: `python scripts/learning_log.py ingest-block --stdin` or skill `learning-capture`
4. Durable domain learning → `knowledge/learnings/<slug>.md`

## Layer 2 — parent (when `link_parent.py` ran)

Parent hooks in `.cursor/hooks.json` capture memory, trajectory, verifier learning. Weekly optional:

`powershell -File 40_operations/scripts/memory_weekly_maintenance.ps1`

Proposals land in parent `30_system/docs/LEARNING_UPDATES.md` via `self_eval_learning_loop.py`.

## Layer 3 — lite auto

- `.agent/learning.jsonl` — session markers (hook) + ingested blocks (CLI)
- `python scripts/learning_log.py summary`

Do not skip layer 1 when layer 2/3 are active — they complement each other.
